Title: Pattiseema will not quench thirst: RRS
Content: The Rayalaseema Rashtra Samithi has advised Chief Minister N. Chandrababu Naidu to look beyond Pattiseema and not project it as the panacea for all the ills plaguing the region.RRS president Kunchem V
Author: Staff Reporter
